  <brief_title>Customized Acoustic Stimulation for Long Term Medical Benefit for the Relief of Tinnitus and Hyperacusis</brief_title>
  <acronym>CALM</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Study of Use of a Customized Acoustic Stimulus to Reduce the Disturbing Symptoms of Tinnitus and Hyperacusis</official_title>
