  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Neuromonics TInnitus Treatment CALM study is a multi site study of 100 adult subjects with
      clinically significant disturbing tinnitus to evaluate outcome measures using the FDA cleared
      Neuromonics treatment after 6, 12, 24 and 36 months. Patients must be meet certain inclusion
      criteria and they are also required to pay for the all costs of the treatment. Subjects will
      be provided a modest participation fee at 6, 12, 24 and 36 months upon completion of patient
      questionnaires (subjects must have access to a computer and internet in order to complete on
      line questionnaires).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
