  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years of age,

          -  TRQ of at least 17 or above,

          -  Able to pay for the treatment,

          -  Not using any other treatment for tinnitus,

          -  Access to computer and internet,

          -  Compliant patient

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hearing PTA &gt; 50 dB, score on HADS of greater than 11 on the anxiety and depression
             scale,

          -  Not willing to follow the protocol
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
